-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">我依家信太子有無辜市民被殺害了</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一句到尾啦，係支共命令&quot;止暴制亂&quot;之下，明知一日拖一日尤其頭七都唔交出足本只會愈拖愈亂，咁都唔交你地話點解呢？？？？</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">加埋依家毛EE爆料，831事件冇人死？？？<br />\n<br />\n<strong></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFYI，當晚現場傳第一消息：有人打死人，但唔係香港警察，你話係邊個呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？？？！！！</span></span></span></strong></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"99134b43ffea6416c1fa3aa1ef9c677e6c058240","tid":1522431,"uid":166947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2fd4b74c6b8d73da5a90b2c67c32796e9992a503","tid":1522431,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T09:46:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>為左殤台個牌為左碗飯，童星老監馮生都要做奶共狗鳥！！！<br />\n<br />\n為紀念燒死林彬而起嘅18樓C座，狗馮既係老監亦負責主要角色，啱啱居然勁做維撚狗，幫狗政Spin話831死人只係街邊八婆鳩吹出黎，又吹香港咁大城市死幾個人點會遮得到！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嘩嘩嘩！！我愈聽愈以為轉左俾Mei西監製添！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins>疑點1: </ins></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n光明正大點解要cap圖唔直接放片？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins><strong>疑點2: </strong></ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n點解Cap既所有圖都唔見畜聾打人，直播又會見到？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins><strong>疑點3: </strong></i